modules.description: This module implements a read-only key-value store interface with operations to query, retrieve, and inspect stored values. It works with string keys and supports data types such as values, dictionaries, and partial content via offset and length parameters. Concrete use cases include accessing versioned configuration data, serving static assets from a precomputed store, and validating content digests for integrity checks.

This module provides a read-only key-value store that supports string keys and value types such as strings, dictionaries, and byte ranges via offset and length. It enables efficient retrieval, inspection, and integrity validation of stored data, supporting use cases like versioned configuration access, static asset serving, and content digest verification. Operations include querying for existence, fetching full or partial values, and inspecting metadata. For example, you can retrieve a configuration entry by key, serve part of a stored asset, or validate content against a known digest.
